*Nastavim* da radim u kancelariji (I will continue to work in the office).
*Nastavila* sam da idem za njim (I continued to follow him).
*Nastavio* sam da pišem pismo (I continued to write the letter).
*Nastavili* smo da se družimo (We continued to hang out).
*Nastaviću* da pokušavam da razumem (I will continue to try to understand).